There's a lot of sand here...

((This is a Job System resource. Click to interact.))
After a long, claustrophobic journey through an unexpectedly long tunnel, you arrive back in the warm, shallows of the Trackless Sea.

The seabed is truly an idyllic scene. Warm, bright, and serene. Small schools of fish swim lazily around, feeding on the local fauna. Despite the pleasantness of the surroundings, you can't seem to shake the feeling that it's not safe here...
